    <title>hexo-theme-next主题升级的时候配置文件冲突解决方法</title>
    <link href="https://www.yangshixian.me/post/f1011520.html"/>
    <id>https://www.yangshixian.me/post/f1011520.html</id>
    <published>2018-08-28T09:33:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-08-28T09:39:45.855Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>hexo-theme-next主题是hexo一个广为使用的主题。当采用git pull 升级的时候，会将master分支拉到本地中，然而 主题配置文件会和我们已经自定义过的配置冲突。官方提供了两个方法</p></blockquote><a id="more"></a><h2 id="next主题github地址"><a href="#next主题github地址" class="headerlink" title="next主题github地址"></a>next主题github地址</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next</a></p><p>当采用git pull 升级的时候，会将master分支拉到本地中，然而 主题配置文件会和我们已经自定义过的配置冲突。官方提供了两个方法：</p><h3 id="1-git-操作命令来解决"><a href="#1-git-操作命令来解决" class="headerlink" title="1. git 操作命令来解决"></a>1. git 操作命令来解决</h3><p><a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/15745045/how-do-i-resolve-git-saying-commit-your-changes-or-stash-them-before-you-can-me/15745424#15745424" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/15745045/how-do-i-resolve-git-saying-commit-your-changes-or-stash-them-before-you-can-me/15745424#15745424</a></p><p>核心命令：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Commit the change using</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m "My message"</span><br><span class="line">Stash it.</span><br><span class="line">Stashing acts as a stack, where you can push changes, and you pop them in reverse order.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">To stash, type</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git stash</span><br><span class="line">Do the merge, and then pull the stash:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git stash pop</span><br><span class="line">Discard the local changes</span><br><span class="line">using git reset --hard</span><br><span class="line">or git checkout -t -f remote/branch</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Or: Discard local changes for a specific file</span><br><span class="line">using git checkout filename</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-用HEXO的DATA-FILES-来解决"><a href="#2-用HEXO的DATA-FILES-来解决" class="headerlink" title="2 用HEXO的DATA-FILES 来解决"></a>2 用HEXO的DATA-FILES 来解决</h3><p>参见 <a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/blob/master/docs/DATA-FILES.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next/blob/master/docs/DATA-FILES.md</a></p><p>推荐方法：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Please ensure you are using Hexo 3 (or above).</span><br><span class="line">Create an file named next.yml in site's hexo/source/_data directory (create _data directory if it did not exists).</span><br><span class="line">And after that steps there are 2 variants, need to choose only one of them and resume next steps.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Variant 2: override: true:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">In next.yml set override option on true.</span><br><span class="line">Copy all NexT theme options from theme's next/_config.yml into hexo/source/_data/next.yml.</span><br><span class="line">Then, in main site's hexo/_config.yml need to define theme: next option (and if needed, source_dir: source).</span><br><span class="line">Use standart parameters to start server, generate or deploy (hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g -d &amp;&amp; hexo s).</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;hexo-theme-next主题是hexo一个广为使用的主题。当采用git pull 升级的时候，会将master分支拉到本地中，然而 主题配置文件会和我们已经自定义过的配置冲突。官方提供了两个方法&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
